(106, 8, 'Jogador', 'Joseph Peterson', 'Joseph Peterson, (born 24 April 1990) is a Haitian football (soccer) player, who currently plays as a center midfielder for Portuguese Liga side SC Braga. Known for having a soft touch on the ball and playing quick one to two touch passes throughout the field, Peterson is known as the Haitian \\"Xavi\\".', NULL),
