(171, 14, 'Jogador', 'João Luiz Ramires Vieira', 'João Luiz Ramires Vieira, known as João Luiz (born December 20, 1985 in Brazil), is a footballer who currently plays as a midfielder for Beira Mar. He made his debut for Marítimo on December 23, 2007 in a 2–1 away victory against União Leiria. His first and so far only goal for the club came in a 4–1 defeat of Sporting Braga at home on April 19, 2008.', NULL),
